# Cloudflare Pages response headers (this file ships in dist/ and Pages reads it).
# Deliberately no CSP: the app inlines its redirect script and the risk/benefit
# of a strict CSP two days before launch is wrong. Revisit post-launch.
/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=(), payment=()
